                     <condition>
                        The under-text, which was erased, is legible in places, including:
                        <quote>
                           ‘notificauerat quod eam uolebat... conferre 
                           aut interdixerat ne conferret... seu illam suae reseruauerat collationi’
                           (fol. 21); ‘uerba legis. complicantes ea et ligantes in fronte, 
                           et quasi coronam capit...’ (fol. 261); ‘uerbum non de secularibus sed de regno Dei’
